{"clientType":"Background","telemetrySchemaVersion":"0.5","component":"Dynamics 365 Business Central Server","componentVersion":"22.0.57579.0","eventId":"RT0005","aadTenantId":"common","environmentType":"Production","longRunningThreshold":"00:00:00.7500000","executionTime":"00:00:01.8120000","sqlStatement":"declare @result int;
                EXEC @result = sp_getapplock @Resource = 'SessionEventTableMaintenance', @LockMode ='Exclusive', @LockTimeout=0;
                IF @result = 0 DELETE FROM [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event]
                  WHERE NOT EXISTS
                  (SELECT 1 FROM
                     [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Active Session] AS acs WITH(NOLOCK) 
                      WHERE
                           acs.[User SID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[User SID]                
                          AND acs.[Server Instance ID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Server Instance ID]
                          AND acs.[Session ID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Session ID]
                          AND acs.[Session Unique ID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Session Unique ID]
                          AND acs.[Login Datetime] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Event Datetime])
                  AND [Event Datetime] < DATEADD(SECOND, -@0, GETUTCDATE()) OR ([Client Type] IN (5, 2) AND [Event Datetime] < DATEADD(SECOND, -@1, GETUTCDATE()))
                  ;"}

{"component":"Dynamics 365 Business Central Server","eventId":"RT0005","telemetrySchemaVersion":"0.5","componentVersion":"22.0.57579.0","clientType":"Background","aadTenantId":"common","environmentType":"Production","sqlStatement":"declare @result int;
                EXEC @result = sp_getapplock @Resource = 'SessionEventTableMaintenance', @LockMode ='Exclusive', @LockTimeout=0;
                IF @result = 0 DELETE FROM [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event]
                  WHERE NOT EXISTS
                  (SELECT 1 FROM
                     [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Active Session] AS acs WITH(NOLOCK) 
                      WHERE
                           acs.[User SID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[User SID]                
                          AND acs.[Server Instance ID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Server Instance ID]
                          AND acs.[Session ID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Session ID]
                          AND acs.[Session Unique ID] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Session Unique ID]
                          AND acs.[Login Datetime] = [SQLDATABASE].[dbo].[Session Event].[Event Datetime])
                  AND [Event Datetime] < DATEADD(SECOND, -@0, GETUTCDATE()) OR ([Client Type] IN (5, 2) AND [Event Datetime] < DATEADD(SECOND, -@1, GETUTCDATE()))
                  ;","longRunningThreshold":"00:00:00.7500000","executionTime":"00:00:00.9820000"}
